{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1702-03_78","head":{"value":"[Madrigal]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", mars 1702 [tome 4], p. 78-79.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Il ne faut pas estre avare, mais l’argent est necessaire pour vivre heureux. C’est ce qui a donné lieu de dire à un homme qui ne paye que d’apparence.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vostre argent n’est jamais de mise","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous sçavez user de remise","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Esperance en vostre maison","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Y déborde à confusion","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si sans l’agreable finance","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On pouvoit vivre d’esperance","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chez les personnes de bon sens","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous meriteriez de l’encens","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}}]}}}